## Summary
Implements automatic token balance refresh in Dashboard. After a transfer is confirmed on-chain, the updated balance is fetched and displayed without manual page refresh.

## Changes
- Added logic in components/Dashboard.tsx (ethers.js + tx.wait())
- Added abis/Token.json (ERC20 ABI)
- Added .env support for REACT_APP_TOKEN_ADDRESS

## Acceptance Criteria
- Balance updates only after tx confirmation
- No page reload required
- Works with testnet or mainnet

## How to test
1. git clone <repo> && cd web3_game_platform
2. git checkout feat/update-balance
3. npm install
4. Create .env file with:
   REACT_APP_TOKEN_ADDRESS=0xYourTokenAddress
5. npm run dev → connect MetaMask → send token → watch balance auto-update

1. Clone & checkout:
   git clone https://github.com/LuckyMan0219/web3_game_platform.git
   cd web3_game_platform
   git fetch origin
   git checkout feat/update-balance

2. Install:
   npm install

3. Environment:
   - Create .env in project root:
     REACT_APP_TOKEN_ADDRESS=0xYourTokenAddress

4. Run:
   npm run dev

5. Open in browser:
   - Connect MetaMask
   - Ensure account has tokens + ETH for gas
   - Transfer tokens → after tx confirmation → balance auto-refreshes
